OL,5, A coalition of 140 organisations and   
OL,6, MPs has called on the government to    
OL,7, consider introducing a social tariff to
OL,8, help with energy bills this winter.    
OL,10,FIn an open letter to Prime Minister    
OL,11,FRishi Sunak, it said support would stop
OL,12,Fpeople having to face a "desperate     
OL,13,Fchoice... between heating and eating". 
OL,15,FAverage household energy bills are set 
OL,16,Fto be 13% higher this winter than they 
OL,17,Fwere last year, it said.               
OL,19,FSocial tariffs are discounted packages 
OL,20,Favailable to low-income households.    
